title: 10/12 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC), Trade Values
description:
We start the show with some Week 6 rankings risers (2:55) and some IDP suggestions (5:52) before analyzing Dave's trade chart (7:45). How does he see the GB backfield evolving rest of season? And are Keenan Allen and Chris Hogan among the elite WRs in Fantasy? ... News and notes (12:30) you need to know including offensive line and defensive injuries that could impact Fantasy ... PIT-KC (22:55), IND-TEN (28:40), LAC-OAK (37:20), LAR-JAC (44:35), NE-NYJ (47:23), CLE-HOU (55:13), CHI-BAL (59:48) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
